m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This +1 flaming composite shortbow grants its wielder the ability to cast flare burst {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spell{/g} three times per day as a 3rd level wizard.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: The wooden surface is covered in thin ornament, the hallmark of Kimiel Tavon, the {mf|baron|baroness|king|queen}'s court master.

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This +4 {g|Encyclopedia:Speed}speed{/g} composite shortbow is decorated with a carving of a hunting cat. It grants its wielder the ability to summon {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d4{/g}+1 smilodons for 15 {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}rounds{/g}.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: The wooden surface is covered in thin ornament, the hallmark of Kimiel Tavon, the {mf|baron|baroness|king|queen}'s court master.

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: When this +4 composite shortbow lands a hit, it grants the target {g|Encyclopedia:Damage_Reduction}DR{/g} 10/melee. It also inflicts a -4 {g|Encyclopedia:Penalty}penalty{/g} to {g|Encyclopedia:Armor_Class}AC{/g} against {g|Encyclopedia:MeleeAttack}melee attacks{/g}, and every melee {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}attack{/g} deals additional 4 {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g} to it.
Whenever this +3 shortbow lands a hit, it has a chance to cast hideous laughter on its target.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: Each time you shoot an arrow with this bow, a terrible pun comes into your head.

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This +5 fey bane shortbow grants its wielder a +4 {g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}bonus{/g} on all {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}saving throws{/g} against the abilities of fey.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: Whenever this bow shoots an arrow, its string hums a quiet melody.

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: Whenever the wielder of this +3 bleed composite shortbow confirms a {g|Encyclopedia:Critical}critical hit{/g} with it, the enemy suffers a stacking -1 {g|Encyclopedia:Penalty}penalty{/g} to {g|Encyclopedia:Armor_Class}AC{/g} until the end of combat.
Whenever this +3 composite shortbow lands a hit on an enemy, the enemy suffers an additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d12{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Damage_Type}piercing damage{/g}.
If the wielder of this +4 {g|Encyclopedia:Speed}speed{/g} composite shortbow has an animal companion or a similar creature, it is affected by a constant haste {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spell{/g} effect.
This is a +1 cold iron ghost touch weapon.

This is a +3 brilliant energy heartseeker weapon. This weapon can tear the soul of a living enemy: whenever it lands a hit, it deals additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d6{/g} force {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: This weapon was once the seat of Finnean's soul. Now that the soul of the Sarkorian Pathfinder has left the weapon, it has fallen silent forever.
